        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1480333569" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12420998601129016448">Great book. I&apos;m always amazed (and envious) when I see how young some of my favorite authors were when they wrote some books I have loved. I think Michael was 26 when he wrote this. It doesn&apos;t fit into my head that I could write like this when I was 26. I don&apos;t think I could write like this now.<br/>Anyway, a good thriller, good pace, intriguing case, good research and explanations. To me, it feels like a bit of a trick, because I think the reader could never guess for sure who was the culprit. <br/>Well,</span>
  <span id="freeText12420998601129016448" style="display:none">Great book. I'm always amazed (and envious) when I see how young some of my favorite authors were when they wrote some books I have loved. I think Michael was 26 when he wrote this. It doesn't fit into my head that I could write like this when I was 26. I don't think I could write like this now.<br />Anyway, a good thriller, good pace, intriguing case, good research and explanations. To me, it feels like a bit of a trick, because I think the reader could never guess for sure who was the culprit. <br />Well, it's a pleasure to read Michael Crichton.</span>
