  <span id="freeText2654654692691235138" style="display:none">I am so happy to have Michael Crichton back in my life, I don't care how long ago this was written. For the time.....it was a very thought provoking book. The end notes were great and also thought provoking. One of my favorite authors, I'm so happy I found his early stuff. You can see where he was always thinking about big issues and how they affected people and government, etc. So happy!</span>
